  Locus:
    Page: 203
    Verse: 14
Tags:
  - Grace
---
The way of grace is mysterious. You struggle for it and you do not get it.
Sometimes, without any struggle, you get it. Its working is governed by
something beyond all laws. It is not bound by any rules, regulations or
conditions.
